+     21: - `BIND_ADDR` - Server bind address (default: `127.0.0.1:8090`)
+     22: - `UUCP_SPOOL` - Paste storage directory (default: `/mnt/data1/spool/uucp/pastebin`)
+     23: - `BASE_PATH` - URL base path for reverse proxy (default: `/pastebin`)
+     24: - `RUST_LOG` - Log level (default: `info`)
+     25: - `PATH` - Must include IPFS binary location for IPFS integration
+     26: 
+     27: ### IPFS Integration
+     28: 
+     29: The service requires `ipfs` command in PATH for automatic IPFS uploads:
+     30: 
+     31: ```bash
+     32: # Verify IPFS is available
